{"tid":2263563,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"審議電訊例 葛珮帆離題批鬥網台","createTime":"2020-10-30T03:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T03:53:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4871050fb306115a5761e4653a66b52fbd526d75","tid":2263563,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:50:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201030/STZEJACOARGERDOYLYI6OFIZME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201030%2FSTZEJACOARGERDOYLYI6OFIZME%2F&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KK0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=be6bba94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201030%2FSTZEJACOARGERDOYLYI6OFIZME%2F&h=b836c158\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201030/STZEJACOARGERDOYLYI6OFIZME/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n審議電訊例 葛珮帆離題批鬥網台<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-4d6S2bvhEYiLpdAUInQmBvJRRI=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ILEW65SV5VFCPDS6P32SBRFQ6Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-4d6S2bvhEYiLpdAUInQmBvJRRI%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FILEW65SV5VFCPDS6P32SBRFQ6Q.jpg&h=29b739de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■葛珮帆昨離題指控網台成為「攬炒派」誤導市民的手段。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】立法會昨恢復二讀《2019年廣播及電訊法例（修訂）條例草案》時，民建聯葛珮帆突將話題扯到要求政府規管網台，雖被立會主席梁君彥指離題，但葛反駁相關修訂是源於傳統電視台和電台受到網台衝擊而提出，資訊科技界立法會議員莫乃光斥葛說法毫無邏輯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建制突襲通過修例<br />\n<br />\n建制派以往已有人提出要規管網台及討論區，葛珮帆發言時借題發揮，聲稱收到很多市民投訴，指有網台主持人使用不雅言詞或者傳播仇恨言論，成為「攬炒派」誤導市民手段，促政府積極研究如何規管網台，維護廣播生態及國家安全等，但梁君彥隨即指葛離題。<br />\n<br />\n專業議政莫乃光發言指，今次修例只放寬跨媒體擁有權，沒有處理保障消費者權益和媒體合併等問題，他又反駁葛珮帆言論，指葛竟然提出電視台選擇少，節目不夠多元化，要透過加強規管網台和網上言論，然後令到節目更加多元化和增加電視台數目，「我真係唔知個邏輯點樣嚟。」<br />\n<br />\n民主派原本積極發言，但建制派施突襲，原打算發言的謝偉銓趁民主派離席要求取消發言，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨尹兆堅解釋，以。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"ef501fbfecc07b39f7a9c63c0cd34fc4486637af","tid":2263563,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:52:18.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">奶共狗<br />\n永世留喺大灣區啦</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0c53dad14e497c04d5ca69c317cc8f006da6981b","tid":2263563,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1212d86ea2047eb24b0c3f6bb09821a0af18f5da","tid":2263563,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNXfLkO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNXfLkO.gif&h=581d87fc&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}